                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17920113-41-defend505 t17920113-41-punish259"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice BULLER.</p>
